snippet.title: Drunk Canary
snippet.description:
Drunk Canary is the world's first and only comedy YouTube channel. Our team of writers all have major personality disorders, allowing them to hyper-focus on creating satire, parody and bits that they are absolutely convinced you'll find so hilarious you'll end up peeing yourself. 

Drunk Canary is also the home of 'The Tomorrow Show' - the award-winning satire show, specializing in unscrupulous rumors, rigorously researched gossip and offensive opinions about celebrities and trends.

Drunk Canary is a run by Sinclair Treadway and Sean Adl-Tabatabai (via their company Shout It Out Limited). We are British-American husband & husband team who love working together to create satirical videos.
